## GOD NODE DETECTION

If the task description mentions OR the touched files contain any god node,
flag `god_nodes:` in the ROUTE block and append `— audit required`.

Full table: see AGENTS.md §God Nodes.

If the human hasn't acknowledged the audit, ask:
`This touches salvatorepesti.com — Personal Portfolio Site (29 edges). Confirm cross-agent audit?`

Quick reference — god nodes by file:
| `salvatorepesti.com.html` | `salvatorepesti.com — Personal Portfolio Site`, `Cloudflare Ecosystem`, `Edge Infrastructure`, `Secure Web Architecture`, `Case 02 — SaaS p95 TTFB Reduction 71%`, `Salvatore Pesti`, `CDN & Caching Strategies`, `Security Auditing & Hardening` |

